ISolution
public class PreferenceSolution
extends UISolution

Concrete implementation of an UISolution that opens a preference page in order to point the user to the place where some erroneous settings may cause a problem.

PreferenceSolution

public PreferenceSolution(ISolution slave,
                          org.eclipse.swt.widgets.Shell shell,
                          java.lang.String preferencePageId)
Construct a new PreferenceSolution for the specified preference page. The parameters for this solution are taken from the slave solution.

Parameters:
slave - The slave solution that should be wrapped by this solution.
shell - The Shell used for the solution.
preferencePageId - The ID of the preference page that should be opened.
